Module fi.tuni.progthree.weatherapp
Package fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp.Model

Class ModelDailyWeatherItem

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp.Model.ModelDailyWeatherItem
public class ModelDailyWeatherItem extends Object
Represents a daily weather item with information about the date, weather icon, temperature range, humidity, and sea level.
